  2. i get to mine by using a computer feature thats already built in, go to

    after that put your VPS ip in the connection box and login with your VPS username and password
    (you made to do a little searching to find the remote desktop access feature it depends on your computer type and what kinda like windows 7/8 etcâ€¦this is for windows 7)
